+Use discovery only.
+
+Search my personal OneDrive, not SharePoint sites, and find all documents related to the integration strategy.
+
+Rules:
+- do not guess any path, drive id, or item id
+- check auth status first
+- search before read
+- only inspect documents returned by the search
+- include documents that are clearly about integration strategy, integration principles, integration architecture, APIs, event-driven integration, data integration, EDM/canonical model, producer-consumer patterns, or EASIKit
+- for each matching document, give me:
+  - file name
+  - location/path
+  - last modified date if available
+  - a one-line reason why it looks relevant
+- do not draft a design or summary yet
+- final output should be just the list of relevant documents

